  <brief_title>A PROMs Based Educational Tool (PROM-DA) for Patients Considering Total Knee Arthroplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>A PROMs Based Educational Tool (PROM-DA) for Patients Considering Total Knee Arthroplasty: Development and a Pilot Randomized Controlled Trial.</official_title>
