  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adult (ageâ‰¥30) patients with knee osteoarthritis (OA)

          -  Have an appointment with a surgeon for consultation about Total Knee Arthroplasty at
             the Edmonton Bone and Joint Centre

          -  Understands, speaks and reads English; and

          -  Able to provide informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Individuals who have had prior total knee arthroplasty

          -  Physician-diagnosed Rheumatoid Arthritis, Psoriatic Arthritis, Ankylosing Spondylitis,
             Fibromyalgia, or Gout.
